<br>
<br>

Today we are excited to announce our first update of 2026!  There is a lot to go through so I will keep this brief, but to sumarise, todays update includes Paralake V6's second major update, a new store that introduces new ways to express yourself, the ability to customize your Bazaar/Business Shop walls, changes to the vehicle system, and much more!  Let's jump in to the changes.
<br>
<br>

[CENTER][IMG size="1920x56"]https://files.perpheads.com/jaWteiRlDgekuOlm.png[/IMG][/CENTER]
<br>
<br>

[SIZE=7][B][U]Map Changes[/U][/B][/SIZE]<br>
Paralake V6.2, whilst smaller in scope than V6.1, still contains a bunch of changes, primarily focused on quality of life, balancing, and visual fidelity.  Before all that though, let's start with the new properties!
<br>
<br>

[CENTER][IMG width="480px" size="1920x1080"]https://files.perpheads.com/OHldokW9S1vxm2wV.png[/IMG][IMG width="480px" size="1920x1080"]https://files.perpheads.com/tZ4ot7l1h1R0zyPR.jpg[/IMG]
[IMG width="480px" size="1920x1080"]https://files.perpheads.com/V6uXHszl37JXyBzy.png[/IMG][IMG width="480px" size="1920x1080"]https://files.perpheads.com/nTEcrqIvl2sms3a1.jpg[/IMG][/CENTER]
<br>
<br>

[SIZE=5][B]Slums Warehouse[/B][/SIZE]<br>
Situated between Road Crew and the Tenement building, this new industrial property offers plenty of space.  This property has 3 doors, 4 chemtable/workbench slots, and can have up to 6 players growing drugs.
<br>
<br>

[SPOILER="Slums Warehouse"]
[IMG width="480px" size="1920x1080"]https://files.perpheads.com/a8itDFti8bIuxHBu.jpg[/IMG][IMG width="480px" size="1920x1080"]https://files.perpheads.com/tZ4ot7l1h1R0zyPR.jpg[/IMG]
[/SPOILER]
<br>
<br>

[SIZE=5][B]City Shop[/B][/SIZE]<br>
A new two floor shop/hangout space in the city, situated just opposite the City gas station.  This is a passive property like the Bazaar/Business Shops and can be used to create a store, a space to roleplay, or just a place to hang out with friends.  It has 2 doors, and has up to 5 workbench slots.
<br>
<br>

[SPOILER="City Shop"]
[IMG width="480px" size="1920x1080"]https://files.perpheads.com/lBPzeFBKFa2YxjhO.jpg[/IMG][IMG width="480px" size="1920x1080"]https://files.perpheads.com/NsDhjbEHZZjMKaJb.jpg[/IMG]
[/SPOILER]
<br>
<br>

[SIZE=5][B]Farm[/B][/SIZE]<br>
This is a complete rework to an old property.  The new Barn situated on the Farm property has a completely new interior, giving this old building a much needed refreshed feel.
<br>
<br>

[SPOILER="Farm"]
[IMG width="480px" size="1920x1080"]https://files.perpheads.com/f0ZsILbzkxH1DS8t.jpg[/IMG][IMG width="480px" size="1920x1080"]https://files.perpheads.com/G6KknHypaBKmtvKz.jpg[/IMG]
[/SPOILER]
<br>
<br>

[SIZE=5][B]Hicktown[/B][/SIZE]<br>
Like Farm, this is another redesign to a classic property.  The new hicktown trailers are designed to look more like caravan trailers.  (Also now with proper lighting).
<br>
<br>

[SPOILER="Hicktown"]
[IMG width="480px" size="1920x1080"]https://files.perpheads.com/nTEcrqIvl2sms3a1.jpg[/IMG][IMG width="480px" size="1920x1080"]https://files.perpheads.com/nCTd7x61LFNwrofM.jpg[/IMG]
[/SPOILER]
<br>
<br>

[B][SIZE=5]Office Complex[/SIZE][/B]<br>
Whilst structuraly the same exterior, the individual floors of Office have received a substantial layout update.  Gone is the large open space, now replaced with a Southgate Center inspired office interior, just with a more modern look.
<br>
<br>

[SPOILER="Office Complex"]
