[B][SIZE=7][U]Custom Shop Wallpapers[/U][/SIZE][/B]<br>
You can now purchase custom wallpapers to apply to your Bazaar/Business Shop.  Wallpapers can be bought from the new Wallpaper World store located just off the Business Plaza.  There are currently 25 wallpapers for to purchase and collect, starting at $50,000 for basic colors, with prices up to £300,000 for more premium designs.  You can then apply these wallpapers when purchasing your shop from the Bank, or by pressing E on your shop's sign.  Applying wallpapers requires you to have Premium.
<br>
<br>

