[B][SIZE=7][U]Vehicle Updates[/U][/SIZE][/B]<br>
We have made some major updates to the vehicle system, plus we have added 2 new vehicles!  One being the Porshe GT3, and the other being a new Police Transit Van.
<br>
<br>

[CENTER][IMG width="456px" size="1231x1000"]https://files.perpheads.com/pd8zHsYHgMb9CfKE.png[/IMG][IMG width="533px" size="878x609"]https://files.perpheads.com/tRcWf1f1KF1RxYMm.png[/IMG][/CENTER]
<br>
<br>

As well as the new vehicles, the following changes have been made to the vehicle systems.
<br>
<br>

[LIST]
[*]Tires now pop independantly, depending on which tire recieves damage.
[*]Tires can be repaired by citizens with the new Tire Repair Kit, purchasable from Safety First.
[*]Introduced new effects for drifting, including sounds and particles.
[*]Added new particles when driving on dirt/grass.
[*]Reworked the emergency light effects on emergency vehicles ([B]Police[/B]: Blue/Red, [B]Medics[/B]: Red/White, [B]Firefighter[/B]: Yellow/Red, [B]Secret Service[/B]: Blue/White, [B]Roadcrew[/B]: Yellow).
[*]Improved the visuals and audio of the car bomb effect.
[*]The car bomb effect now occours in the skybox.
[*]Indicators now turn off automatically after a turn.
[*]Indicators now flash at different speeds.
[*]Added check engine light to the default speedometer.
[*]Improved the models for the following vehicles: Bugatti Veyron 16.4, McLaren F1, Ferrari LaFerrari, Dodge Viper, and Volkswagen Beetle 1967.
[*]Improved vehicle metal textures.
[*]Gas pumps now hide the pump nozzle when during refuling.
[/LIST]
<br>
<br>

[CENTER][IMG size="1920x56"]https://files.perpheads.com/jaWteiRlDgekuOlm.png[/IMG][/CENTER]
<br>
<br>

[B][SIZE=7][U]New Daily Missions[/U][/SIZE][/B]<br>
We are introducing new daily missions this update.  Every day you will receive 2 legal missions.  One with the goal of catching a certain type of fish, and the other a mission related to a specific job.
<br>
<br>

[CENTER][IMG width="435px" size="472x426"]https://files.perpheads.com/4HU8dJFlQgC0dqWO.jpg[/IMG][/CENTER]
<br>
<br>

The daily job missions are:
<br>
<br>

[LIST]
[*][B]Courier[/B]: Deliever a certain amount of packages
[*][B]Firefighter[/B]: Extinguish a certain amount of fires and heal a certain number of citizens
[*][B]Medic[/B]: Revive a certain number of citizens, heal a certain number of citizens
[*][B]Roadcrew[/B]: Repair a certain number of vehicles, impound a certain number of vehicles
[/LIST]
<br>
<br>

[CENTER][IMG size="1920x56"]https://files.perpheads.com/jaWteiRlDgekuOlm.png[/IMG][/CENTER]
<br>
<br>

